hint-mode
=========

Portions of the clickable-element detection and click-simulation logic in
`@sannagroup/hint-mode` are derived from Vimium:

  https://github.com/philc/vimium
  Licensed under the MIT License.
  Copyright (c) Phil Crosby and Vimium contributors.

Specifically, the rules in `clickable-elements.ts` mirror Vimium's
`getLocalHintsForElement` (`content_scripts/link_hints.js`), and the
seven-event simulated-click sequence in `click-simulator.ts` mirrors
Vimium's `simulateClick` (`lib/dom_utils.js`).
